{"tid":1493514,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！88歲黃夏蕙   「積極考慮」出擊灣仔修頓區選","createTime":"2019-08-21T09:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T11:44:25.000Z","uid":221265,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"592f125da31cf8c87bb6e757194bea817f2e88d4","tid":1493514,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:20:27.000Z","msg":"嘩！<br />\n有無巴打係修頓選區？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝人「夏蕙姨」黃夏蕙表態有意參戰今年 11 月舉行的區議會選舉。她今日凌晨在Facebook專頁發文，表示對有被捕長者虐打一事感到「痛心疾首」，並且代濫暴警員向受害者道歉。同時，她疑似預告加入即將在11月舉行的區議會選舉的戰團，指自己有意在灣仔修頓球場「出發」，改變社區不公，讓居民重拾和諧社區生活。經理人接受查詢時則表示她「積極考慮」參選。<br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙在帖文提及有意在灣仔修頓球場區「出發」，服務和集合身邊所有，改變社區的一切不公平的事情，重新將之前和階（諧）社區生活還給市民」，疑似預告參選即將在11月舉行的區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》就此向其經理人查詢，經理人表示黃夏蕙會積極考慮參選即將在11月舉行的區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙亦在帖文表示，對有被捕長者在醫院內被軍裝警員虐打，感到「痛心疾首」，並對受害者與家人衷心慰問，亦代「虐待伯伯的人」向受害者道歉，希望他「康復後原諒他們的罪孽和無知」。她同時質疑「點解要向一位63嵅（歲）的伯伯作出如此虐待和損害個人應有的尊嚴！」。<br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙有意「出發」的灣仔修頓球場，屬於「修頓選區」，現任區議員為報稱獨立，過去在2007年起，連續三屆連任，亦曾在區議會投票支持《一國兩制白皮書》及人大831決定的<span style=\"color: red;\">李碧儀</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLN1n5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLN1n5.jpg&h=b64ca008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙並非首度透露從政意願，2015 年提透露有意參與區議會選舉。但經考慮後，她表示自己關心社會議題，新界東北發展及機場第三條跑道都有留意，希望有場合讓她好好發表意見，但區議會的舞台未夠大，所以她決定不選區議會，只會考慮立法會選舉，她最終未有參與上屆立法會選舉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnH1mnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnH1mnP.jpg&h=687d2d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvbNgVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvbNgVH.png&h=05eab053&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6d37cb9cb3f68b0f1916fc864186c3f5c81104f","tid":1493514,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"補返條link先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/積極考慮-戰區選-黃夏蕙-有意灣仔修頓-出發/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-%E6%88%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8-%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99-%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E4%BF%AE%E9%A0%93-%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%2F&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9ogESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=b919bbbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-%E6%88%B0%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8-%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%8F%E8%95%99-%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E4%BF%AE%E9%A0%93-%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%2F&h=de64ec4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/積極考慮-戰區選-黃夏蕙-有意灣仔修頓-出發/</a>"},{"pid":"fbc731a0a56a96e28ba18724f4ccf0d472ac68dc","tid":1493514,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"不過咁老有心有無力㗎？"},{"pid":"8da6cf0d95cb6bba4cce7f8b2d16d07be6ed6611","tid":1493514,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbc731a0a56a96e28ba18724f4ccf0d472ac68dc","tid":1493514,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"不過咁老有心有無力㗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"到時選到就請助理㗎啦"},{"pid":"b251cde0544bb010e583f049bab725de55711f50","tid":1493514,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"0beeae288d03d7f77fc0d2f72c0e2f23f2b1f559","tid":1493514,"uid":37668,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"仲小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c03df52057a578c5ed4a899edcf632ab053af27","tid":1493514,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm